 paddock-tui                                                        ns: default                    
  Sessions (0)              │ (no session selected — pick one in the sidebar or press n to create) 
   [+ new session]          │                                                                      
  Active: 0                 │                                                                      
 ↑↓ select · Enter type · n new · e end · / search · q/Ctrl-C quit · ? help                        

╭─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
│                                                                             │
│  paddock-tui keybindings                                                    │
│                                                                             │
│  sidebar:                                                                   │
│    ↑↓ / jk    move selection                                                │
│    Enter      type a prompt (or open new-session modal on [+ new session])  │
│    n          new session                                                   │
│    e          end session                                                   │
│    /          filter                                                        │
│    q / Ctrl-C quit                                                          │
│                                                                             │
│  prompt:                                                                    │
│    Enter      submit prompt (queues if a run is in flight)                  │
│    Ctrl-J     newline (multi-line prompt)                                   │
│    Ctrl-E     open $EDITOR                                                  │
│    Ctrl-X     cancel in-flight run                                          │
│    Ctrl-R     toggle raw events                                             │
│                                                                             │
│  main pane:                                                                 │
│    PgUp/PgDn  scroll run history                                            │
│    Home/End   snap to top / bottom                                          │
│    mouse wheel  also scrolls (hold Shift for native terminal scroll)        │
│                                                                             │
│  slash commands (in prompt):                                                │
│    :cancel     cancel in-flight run                                         │
│    :queue      show queued prompts                                          │
│    :template T set last-template                                            │
│    :status     compact session summary                                      │
│    :interactive (reserved — not yet implemented)                            │
│    :help       this screen                                                  │
│                                                                             │
│  Esc / ?: close this help                                                   │
│                                                                             │
╰─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯